function applyThreshold(pixel::Int)
    if pixel > 200
        return 0
    else
        return 1
    end
end

for i in 1:nRows
    for j in 1:nCols
        field[i,j]=applyThreshold(imgi[i*res,j*res])
    end

function drawBalls(drawing, grid)
    nRows, nCols = size(grid)
    stepX, stepY = 10,10
    circScale = min(nRows, nCols) / max(nRows, nCols)
    points = Array{NamedTuple}(undef, nRows, nCols)
    
    for i in 1:nRows
        for j in 1:nCols
            if grid[i,j] == 0
                sethue("white")
            else
                sethue("black")
            end
            
            pos = Point(stepX *(j - 1), stepY*(i - 1))
            circle(pos, 2.5 * circScale, :fill)
            points[i,j] = (x = pos.x, y = pos.y, val=grid[i,j])
        end
    end
    
    return points
end

function iso_line(isoValue, north, east, south, west)
    if isoValue == 0 || isoValue == 15
    elseif isoValue == 1
        line(west,south, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 2
        line(south, east, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 3 || isoValue == 12
        line(west, east, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 4 || isoValue == 11
        line(north, east, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 5
        line(north, west, :stroke)
        line(east, south, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 6 || isoValue == 9
        line(north, south, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 7 || isoValue == 8
        line(north, west, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 10
        line(north, east, :stroke)
        line(south, west, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 13
        line(east, south, :stroke)
    elseif isoValue == 14
        line(west,south,:stroke)
    end
end
